e=A.H("The project involves researchers, practitioners, and clients at Laval University, Montreal University, the Institut Nazareth et Louis-Braille (INLB), Lethbridge-Layton-Mackay Rehabilitation Center, Regroupement des aveugles et amblyopes du Montr\xe9al m\xe9tropolitain (RAAMM), and \u201cCentre interdisciplinaire de recherche en r\xe9adaptation et int\xe9gration sociale\u201d (CIRRIS). The expertise of the team touched the fields of optometry, assistive technology,  rehabilitation, and design in  arts and technology.",A.x(g8,g8,g8,g8,g8,g8))
