a0=A.q(g8,a0,g8)
a3=A.H("* When accessing a webpage through a screen reader, much of the visually available information is lost to VI users or has to be kept in memory at all times (as opposed to just looking at the screen again). \n* Designing technology for users with a completely different experience of the world has to be done carefully to avoid ill-fitted or patronizing devices.\n* Development in the AT field can be slow as it often fails to compete with more financially attractive fields, negatively impacting the cost, availability, support for an AT. ",A.x(g8,g8,g8,g8,g8,g8))
a4=r.w
