a4=A.q(g8,a4,g8)
a7=A.H("* Providing a persistent, interactive, and nonvisual (tactile) representation of a webpage to improve the navigation experience of visually impaired users.\n* The participatory design approach, where the research team, clinicians, and target users are involved in the conception, construction, improvement, and evaluation of the technology to assess the technology aligns with the needs and realities of the target population.\n* Launching an organization around the project as a platform to connect academics, developers, users, and enthusiasts of tactile technology from different fields.\n",A.x(g8,g8,g8,g8,g8,g8))
