b9=A.H("* Audio-only screen readers are the AT of choice of about 80% of VI internet users.\n* Getting an overview of the webpage, navigating and learning its structure, and skipping to their favorite content are common pain points of the experience of VI internet users. \n* There are no open-source tactile stimulation devices available for this kind of development. \n",A.x(g8,g8,g8,g8,g8,g8))
